OL,3,CWildfire breaks out on North Wales
OL,4,Cmountainside
OL,6,FResidents have been warned to keep
OL,7,Faway from the scene of a wildfire near
OL,8,FLlanbedr, in Gwynedd.
OL,10,FA wildfire has broken out across the
OL,11,FNorth Wales mountainside in Gwynedd,
OL,12,Fwith rescue services responding to the
OL,13,Fblaze.
OL,15,FFire crews have been responding to
OL,16,Fseveral blazes across North wales this
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
