OL,3,CWildfire breaks out on North Wales
OL,4,Cmountainside
OL,6,FThe blaze is close to the site of a
OL,7,Fwildfire that broke out on Sunday (12
OL,8,FJuly) on Conwy mountain, which
OL,9,Faffected around 200 acres of land with
OL,10,Fsome residents in the village of
OL,11,FCapelulo having to evacuate their
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,FThe major incident declared on Conwy
OL,15,Fmountain has now been brought under
OL,16,Fcontrol.
OL,18,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,19,Fhas confirmed that they are in
OL,20,Fattendance at Llanbedr, in Gwynedd and
OL,21,FConwy mountain, near Capelulo.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
