OL,3,CWildfire breaks out on North Wales
OL,4,Cmountainside
OL,6,FThey say the incidents are under
OL,7,Fcontrol but have urged people in the
OL,8,Faffected areas to keep their windows
OL,9,Fclosed.
OL,11,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fsaid: "Residents affected by smoke are
OL,13,Fadvised to keep windows and doors
OL,14,Fclosed until conditions improve and
OL,15,Fthe smoke has dispersed.
OL,17,F"Once the smoke has cleared it is a
OL,18,Fgood idea to open windows and doors to
OL,19,Fair your home."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
